We need to figure out a good way to do democratic-
socialism.  We need to find a better way, the best
way, to do democratic-socialism right.  If we seek
the better way, I believe that we can find it.  We
are social animals; we are political animals; and
we are problemsolving animals.

We are social beings, and we are social creatures.
We are the creations of the society we live in.
If we live in a selfish and greedy society, then
we will be the selfish creatures, the greedy
creations of such a society.  If we seem to be
more selfish than selfless, then we are the
creations of a selfish social environment.  We
have adapted ourselves to a selfish milieu.  We
have adapted to this milieu in order to survive
and prosper.

